PrecisAuthority (a) to enter into three AGREEMENTS with the Government of the YUKON TERRITORY which provide for (i) the transfer of responsibility for the operation, maintenance and reconstruction of certain segments of the ALASKA HIGHWAY, (ii) the making of a separate contribution towards the reconstruction of the highway between Watson Lake to Whitehorse, (iii) the provision of ENGINEERING SERVICES with respect to the reconstruction of the SHAKWAK section, and (b) to transfer Crown highway maintenance equipment.
